Oldies 98.1 FM. Suffolk County's Good Time Oldies. Enable our skill then say "Alexa open oldies ninety eight one".

"Suffolk Country's Good Time Oldies" is JVC Broadcasting's brand new radio station featuring the Top 40 hits of the 50's 60's 70's & 80's just as you remember them! From your favorite Motown Memories, Elvis Presley, the Beatles, Elton John, Fleetwood Mac, Hall & Oates, Huey Lewis & so many more! More information found at www.oldies981.com.
